Title: Khamuls Tower
Text: Lady Galadriel asked me to help her discovering the truth behind the return of the withking. If both are back, that all of them are!I have to go to the Tower of Khamul in the east in Eryn Garan and take a look if its empty! .. I hope it is! I don't want to fight a ghost!
CompleteText: Here it is the tower of the Nazgul Khamul!I can see light inside, I should go and take a look. I feel like I'm being watched! I have to be careful!
